node.text: @dressacake Too far for us to travel there to pick up...! 😅
@esth3r_esth3r Ya, that why now at least hv delivery.

Day 32 of Circuit Breaker.⁣
⁣
I have been drooling at the pictures from @leptonyxscript whenever he visits @ahhuateochewnoodle.  I have always wanted to try the noodles but the location is so far at the West!!! Imagine my excitement when I knew that they have islandwide delivery during this circuit breaker period! ⁣
⁣
Didn’t get to place an order last week as they are closed on public holiday. I finally placed my order for this week as they deliver to North-East today. ⁣
⁣
Feature here:⁣
Siganture BTM $5.20⁣
𝐌𝐞𝐞𝐩𝐨𝐤 $𝟓.20⁣
𝐌𝐞𝐞𝐤𝐢𝐚 $𝟓.20⁣
⁣
Delivery for North-East is $10⁣
No minimum order. Whatsapp 88150716 to place your order. ⁣
⁣
Check out the cute notes from Jean in the last picture. 😊⁣
⁣
⁣
📍 𝔸𝕙 ℍ𝕦𝕒 𝕋𝕖𝕠𝕔𝕙𝕖𝕨 𝔽𝕚𝕤𝕙𝕓𝕒𝕝𝕝 ℕ𝕠𝕠𝕕𝕝𝕖⁣
415 Pandan Garden⁣
#01-117⁣
7am-3pm, close on Sundays and Public Holidays⁣
